自2019年7月8日起'''[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]同性婚姻'''正式合法並開放註冊。

2008年厄瓜多爾憲法容許民事結合<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.365gay.com/news/new-ecuador-constitution-includes-gay-rights-guarantees |title=New Ecuador constitution includes gay rights guarantees |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2011-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605124217/http://www.365gay.com/news/new-ecuador-constitution-includes-gay-rights-guarantees |dead-url=yes }}</ref>並於2009年9月正式生效。第一宗民事結合於同年10月舉行。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogdelimagay.blogspot.com/2009/10/se-realizo-primeraunion-civil.html |title=Se realizó primera unión civil homosexual en Ecuador |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2011-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111009104302/http://blogdelimagay.blogspot.com/2009/10/se-realizo-primeraunion-civil.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.elsalvador.com/mwedh/nota/nota_opinion.asp?idCat=6342&idArt=4068556 |title=Legalización de uniones homosexuales en Ecuador |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2011-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615025825/http://www.elsalvador.com/mwedh/nota/nota_opinion.asp?idCat=6342&idArt=4068556 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sentidog.com/article.php?id_news=25118 |title=Se realizó primera unión civil homosexual en Ecuador |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2009-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091018035515/http://www.sentidog.com/article.php?id_news=25118 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.eradio.com.mx/enews/?noticia=5237 |title=Ecuador celebró la primera unión de hecho entre personas del mismo sexo, desatando la indignación de la iglesia católica |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722223205/http://www.eradio.com.mx/enews/?noticia=5237 |archive-date=2011-07-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dosmanzanas.com/2009/10/ecuador-celebro-la-primera-union-de-hecho-entre-personas-del-mismo-sexo-desatando-la-indignacion-de-la-iglesia-catolica.html |title=Ecuador celebró la primera unión de hecho entre personas del mismo sexo, desatando la indignación de la iglesia católica |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2012-09-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ATSE1e6r?url=http://www.dosmanzanas.com/2009/10/ecuador-celebro-la-primera-union-de-hecho-entre-personas-del-mismo-sexo-desatando-la-indignacion-de-la-iglesia-catolica.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2019年6月12日，厄瓜多尔最高法院裁定支持同性婚姻，其判決書於7月8日公告讓同性婚姻正式生效並開放註冊。<ref name="star">{{cite web|url=https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/ecuador-court-delays-ruling-same-sex-marriage/|title=Ecuador high court delays ruling on same-sex marriage|work=Gay Star News|date=2019-06-04|last=Crittenton|first=Anya|accessdate=2019-06-14|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620233138/https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/ecuador-court-delays-ruling-same-sex-marriage/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tele">{{cite web|url=https://www.telesurtv.net/news/corte-constitucional-ecuador-matrimonio-igualitario-20190604-0031.html|title=Corte Constitucional de Ecuador aplaza decisión sobre matrimonio igualitario|work=telesur|date=2019-06-04|language=es|accessdate=2019-06-14|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608075131/https://www.telesurtv.net/news/corte-constitucional-ecuador-matrimonio-igualitario-20190604-0031.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/06/13/americas/ecuador-same-sex-marriage-intl/index.html|title=Ecuador's highest court legalizes same-sex marriage|last=CNN|first=Kara Fox and Ana Melgar Zuniga|website=CNN|access-date=2019-06-13|archive-date=2019-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619062310/https://www.cnn.com/2019/06/13/americas/ecuador-same-sex-marriage-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://cuencahighlife.com/ecuador-records-first-official-same-sex-marriages-as-court-ruling-goes-into-effect|title=Ecuador records first official same-sex marriages as court ruling goes into effect|work=CuencaHighLife|date=2019-07-09|accessdate=2019-07-11|archive-date=2019-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190710234732/https://cuencahighlife.com/ecuador-records-first-official-same-sex-marriages-as-court-ruling-goes-into-effect/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

